{"tid":534431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全台最大糖果工廠用逾期原料  外銷產品流入香港及澳門","createTime":"2018-01-19T18:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T05:31:11.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab8313119a6289873298431d5d24e70f671a79a","tid":534431,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"【全台最大糖果工廠用逾期原料】 <br />\n【外銷產品流入香港及澳門】<br />\n<br />\n台灣最大糖果工廠，被揭發使用過期原料，逾 5 噸問題產品流入市面，部分更外銷到香港及澳門。<br />\n<br />\n當地衛生局及地檢署人員到位於台中的工場，封存逾期原料及問題糖果。<br />\n<br />\n當局去年接報稱，有 30 年歷史的宜農生物科技，使用逾期果汁、香料等製作糖果，部分原料逾期半年以上。<br />\n<br />\n工廠估計，過去半年生產逾 5 噸問題產品，絕大部分已流入 6 個縣市、香港及澳門等地。<br />\n<br />\n局方勒令問題食品全部下架，宜農亦安排顧客辦理退貨，公司面臨最高 2 億新台幣罰款。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#台灣　#糖果工廠　#過期原料 #流入市面　#外銷　#香港<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/788067688051968/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F788067688051968%2F&d=jgwfxsZ53oHshNhi0wrQji7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=75d7406c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/788067688051968/</a>"},{"pid":"25aa1e8b67b3dd1d600b11decc6809a9af8c51ea","tid":534431,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:45:47.000Z","msg":"所以咪話"},{"pid":"2c8bfab3f824da1e1c06b00de840880a45f8af7a","tid":534431,"uid":28028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:48:45.000Z","msg":"最大個間都出得事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0112987286d6a8a452e5eeb4dbcfa962d4bfcfa6","tid":534431,"uid":2373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:57:30.000Z","msg":"繁體支那"},{"pid":"f84964f5ee1341b24ec8ea85b6225e629ee8e577","tid":534431,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T19:01:09.000Z","msg":"中國台灣一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc0498996a6f872b81ad6885a09a2e2ee5d5b5f","tid":534431,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0